		<title>02Farm Mechanisation &amp; Yields</title>
		<content>{Computers}are now used on many farms  
 for financial management and stock    
 control.                              
                                       
 As verges have been ploughed and      
 ditches potted, fields have been      
 merged and many {hedgerows}have       
 disappeared.                          
                                       
 Harvesting has greatly benefitted from
{mechanisation}and work often continues
 right into the night.                 
                                       
{Yields per acre}are reaching the      
 following figures:                    
                                       
    Wheat         3\ to  4 tonne       
    Oilseed rape  1  to  2 tonne       
    Potatoes     18  to 22 tonne       
                                       
                                       
                                       </content>
